<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h1 class="fw-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">
            CogniHub values the privacy and confidentiality of employee and organizational data.
            The system is designed for internal payroll management and is accessible only to authorized users.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 px-4 py-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-3">🔒 Data Collection</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        CogniHub collects employee information such as name, designation, salary structure,
                        and payroll records strictly for payroll processing and statutory reporting purposes.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 px-4 py-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-3">👥 Data Access</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        Access to information in CogniHub is restricted according to user roles and responsibilities.
                        Administrators and HR are responsible for managing employee onboarding, profile updates, and approvals,
                        while individual employees can view only their own payroll and attendance data.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 px-4 py-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-3">🛡️ Data Security</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        CogniHub enforces secure authentication and authorization mechanisms to protect payroll data
                        from unauthorized access or modification. System activity may be logged and monitored
                        so that administrators can review usage and support internal audit requirements.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 px-4 py-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-3">🚫 Data Sharing</h5>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        Payroll and employee data is not shared with third parties except where required by law.
                        Information is used strictly within the organization in accordance with internal
                        policies and applicable regulations.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                By using CogniHub, users acknowledge and agree to this privacy policy.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
